{"TopicId":68207,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Fly-by camera","CreatedByName":"Azimech","CreatedById":50750,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-05T12:58:18Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Azimech","CreatedById":50750,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-05T12:58:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIn most aerial simulations there is the option to place an external camera floating in a fixed position somewhere in front of an airplane, a beautiful effect as it roars past.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOften they did it in Star Trek as well, with a big SHOOOSH sound. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI miss that in KSP. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESometimes the camera should be moving with the object in focus with a somewhat speed, otherwise you wouldn\u0027t see a thing if it flies by with 2 km/s.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHere\u0027s a short video with some fly-by\u0027s from my favourite WW2 simulation, IL2 Sturmovik: \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022459\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/GQ6ek0Gt5Bs?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAnd one of the most iconic departures in history:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/-p1hxvPOIhE?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kruleworld","CreatedById":69697,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-06T08:11:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Estatic position camera...hmm, good idea. it could default to be at the KSP, so you can watch the take-off from the ground.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://cloud-4.steampowered.com/ugc/579018555208685132/2162E17190DC3582E4734CE5D154BBA11402A564/\u0022 alt=\u00222162E17190DC3582E4734CE5D154BBA11402A564\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GTC","CreatedById":108468,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-27T02:50:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u002B1. I play a lot of flight sims and this is a must have!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bill Phil","CreatedById":127797,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-27T03:10:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIt would make cinematics a lot easier...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI agree.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"nli2work","CreatedById":106805,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-11-27T03:27:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/94171\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/94171\u003C/a\u003E\n"}]}